body:
i compiled pytorch and onnx from source of both master branch, and run offical demo is ok.
but on my code has error as follow:
1. first i get a pritrained model from github, which trained use torch.nn.parallel.DataParallel and when use torch.nn.export this is error, so i follow one guid as follow delete the prefix : "module:" then the load and export is ok.
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6283983/44339905-b8b97d80-a4b5-11e8-9461-c6cf489a2150.png)
2. when i use onnx load the export model, do onnx.check_model(""), it has follow error:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6283983/44339967-eacadf80-a4b5-11e8-81de-9cad63b169ae.png)
3. my model has follow define , did this map and reduce cause the error?
the model define line https://github.com/lixx2938/MegaDepth/blob/master/pytorch_DIW_scratch.py
